  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2>Cats Don't Speak\" is a horror mystery game with urban legend theme. The story takes place in an abandoned experimental high school, a mystery interview involved some old stories, as the investigation deepens, the school of those unknown, buried for a long time the bloody story slowly emerge, piecing together a chilling truth ......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e8eecf2901cd93972c69119aabdb8bab.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e8eecf2901cd93972c69119aabdb8bab.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e8eecf2901cd93972c69119aabdb8bab.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game screen</h2>Old-style retro painting style, depressing horror atmosphere, heartbeat accelerates, blood pressure rises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/5d45c4c671ed5967d359df0a705f88a8.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/5d45c4c671ed5967d359df0a705f88a8.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/5d45c4c671ed5967d359df0a705f88a8.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/4.GIF?t=1754569809\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game content</h2>The work is partly based on real events in society, combined with the producer's own experience, is the first in the urban legend series.<br>The retribution of good and evil, like shadow, three lives of karma, the cycle is not lost.<br>Each decision within the game may affect the ending of the game, the game has multiple endings.<br>The puzzles in the game are well designed in terms of difficulty and are not too difficult to advance the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e703789045366cabfa813c800698a596.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e703789045366cabfa813c800698a596.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e703789045366cabfa813c800698a596.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2>Cats Don't Speak\" is a horror mystery game with urban legend theme. The story takes place in an abandoned experimental high school, a mystery interview involved some old stories, as the investigation deepens, the school of those unknown, buried for a long time the bloody story slowly emerge, piecing together a chilling truth ......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e8eecf2901cd93972c69119aabdb8bab.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e8eecf2901cd93972c69119aabdb8bab.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e8eecf2901cd93972c69119aabdb8bab.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game screen</h2>Old-style retro painting style, depressing horror atmosphere, heartbeat accelerates, blood pressure rises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/5d45c4c671ed5967d359df0a705f88a8.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/5d45c4c671ed5967d359df0a705f88a8.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/5d45c4c671ed5967d359df0a705f88a8.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/4.GIF?t=1754569809\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game content</h2>The work is partly based on real events in society, combined with the producer's own experience, is the first in the urban legend series.<br>The retribution of good and evil, like shadow, three lives of karma, the cycle is not lost.<br>Each decision within the game may affect the ending of the game, the game has multiple endings.<br>The puzzles in the game are well designed in terms of difficulty and are not too difficult to advance the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e703789045366cabfa813c800698a596.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e703789045366cabfa813c800698a596.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/e703789045366cabfa813c800698a596.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
